{%- comment -%}
  Yerba Magic — long-form product story / conversion content.
  Framework: 3-4 colors max (green, strawberry pink, gold) over alternating
  light (cream) and dark (ink) backgrounds. Recoleta headings / Volte body.
  All icons are inline SVG (rounded line icons, currentColor). No emoji.
{%- endcomment -%}

